entry.tran: 不成功的；落空的；失败的
entry.def: Something that is unsuccessful does not achieve what it was intended to achieve.

example.ex: ...a second unsuccessful operation on his knee...

entry.tran: （尤指事业上）失败的，不成功的
entry.def: Someone who is unsuccessful does not achieve what they intended to achieve, especially in their career.
